The paper deals with motion planning for robots, which is a core topic in robotics (cs.RO). The proposed algorithm couples perception and motion planning, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm also utilizes optimization techniques, which fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY).
